<statement>
<p>What are the solutions to <m>\displaystyle-{4}{\left({x}+{2}\right)}^{{2}}+{20}={0}</m>? <fillin characters="12" /></p>
<p>Round solutions to two decimal places.</p>

</statement>
<solution>
<p><ul><li>0.24,-4.24</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle-{4}{\left({x}+{2}\right)}^{{2}}+{20}={0}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{4}{\left({x}+{2}\right)}^{{2}}=-{20}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{\left({x}+{2}\right)}^{{2}}={5}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}+{2}=\pm{2.2360679774998}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=-{2}\pm{2.2360679774998}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}={0.23606797749979},-{4.2360679774998}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}={0.24},-{4.24}</m></p>
</solution>
</myopenmath>

